						               													<description>A Romanian strategy game for 2-6 players. You need to build as many highways as you can but be careful! Your opponents will sabotage you with unexpected incidents: a broken viaduct, an appeal to the public auction, blocking the works and see if you can repel the attack of opponents with negotiations, allocation of funds, any new builder or with some electoral promises.&amp;#10;It is recommended for 14+ years old players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;How to play:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;     Cards with cities will be shuffled and equally distributed for all players. If any cards remain undistributed, you need to put them in a separate stack on the table.&amp;#10;     Cards with vignette will be stacked on the table.&amp;#10;     Cards with sabotage actions will be shuffled and given 10 to every player (if there are 6 players, any of them will be given 8 cards). The rest are placed on the table.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All players start from Bucharest and roll the dice. They need to move their pawn an equal number of points as corresponding on the dice (but he can't step twice on the same point in a turn). If the pawn is placed on a highway point, the player can ask for the related card, by initiating an act of sabotage against the player who owns that card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;What is sabotage:&amp;#10;Sabotage cards have a number of points (e.g.: 1 / 2 / 8 / 0.1 or -3 / -5 etc). A player who wants a card for a highway, needs to put down a sabotage card of negative value (e.g.: -3). The opponent must repel the attack with 1 or more cards with positive value until their sum is greater than the opponent's card (-1 equals +1 or overcome with +2). In case of equality, challenged player can keep his card. Otherwise, if the challenged player overcomes the attack, he can choose a card with cities from the player who initiated the attack. If the challenged player is defeated, the player who initiated the attack receives his requested card.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Vignette cards: &amp;#10;Can be used only at border crossing points in order to obtain 3 sabotage cards OR to ask for any of highway city cards.&amp;#10;Every route has a specific number of points. The player with most points wins.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
